                    name:'Amoeba proteus',latin:'Amoeba proteus',era:'Proterozoic',
                    desc:'The iconic shape-shifting single-celled predator. Moves by extending pseudopods and engulfs bacteria by surrounding them — the same process human immune cells use to destroy pathogens.',
